name: In the Cave of the Mountain Demon King OG.mp3
description:
Thé original .mp3 file to m'y personal favorite song I ever wrote. Found on the album "Chrysalis Transition" - which has been stolen multiple times for *Checks notes* "meditation CDs?" - Doesn't get closer to the original archive than before I even made the .FLAC version.
That violin... PreWWI Medio Fino that I vigorously twisted the legs so I can at least make music with it before Florida humidity makes it completely unplayable. My great grandfather's brother bought it used and was the only thing of value he left behind when he got hit by a train. Passed down to me as the only musician in the family. Truly this honora its legacy more than it being sawdust falling apart in high humidity; and His legacy.
